data.chText: 没有成果的；无成效的；徒然的
我们努力说服她，但毫无成效。
data.enText: Our efforts to persuade her proved fruitless.

ex.chText: 他做了膝盖手术，徒劳地指望能进入该队。
ex.enText: He underwent a knee operation in the vain hope of getting into the team.

ex.chText: 她仰起头，却无法忍住眼泪。
ex.enText: She raised her head in a vain attempt to hold back the tears.

synonyms.bx: 指努力、希望、搜寻等未能获得想要的结果的。

ex.chText: 由较大公司提出的夭折了的并购
ex.enText: an abortive takeover bid by the larger firm

ex.chText: 没有关于那次未遂的军事政变的记录。
ex.enText: There is no record of the abortive military coup.

synonyms.bx: 指行动、计划等没有成功的。

ex.chText: 到目前为止，他们的研究工作毫无结果。
ex.enText: So far, their research has been fruitless.

ex.chText: 试图解决争端的努力白费了，这让他很失望。
ex.enText: The fruitless attempt to settle the dispute disappointed him.

synonyms.bx: 尤指付出很多努力却无成效的。

ex.chText: 军队没有起到保护当地平民的作用。
ex.enText: The army has proved ineffective in protecting the local civilians.

ex.chText: 这种特效去污剂基本去不掉汤渍。
ex.enText: This special stain remover was almost ineffective in removing the soup stain.

ex.chText: 事实证明该政策未能解决问题。
ex.enText: The policy proved ineffective in dealing with the problem.

synonyms.bx: 侧重指人或事物未能发挥应有之作用的。

synonym.guide: 导航词义：未能达到目的的

example: futile years after her artistic peak

value.def: Fruitless actions, events, or efforts do not achieve anything at all.

example.ex: Talks have so far have been fruitless.
example.tran: 会谈到目前为止未见成果。

value.tran: 无结果的;无成效的;徒劳的

example.ex: Four years of negotiation ended fruitlessly last December.
example.tran: 历时4 年的谈判在去年 12 月无果而终。
